INSTALL:

First install hs-plugins and fps.

The following is a guide to install lambdabot on your computer. Begin by
unpacking the lambdabot archive into a directory and modify the file
Config.hs to suit your needs. Then run:

	autoconf
	./configure
	make	(gmake on some systems)

KNOWN BUGS:

The following bugs are currently known to the lambdabot developer team. We
are working on them:

* @topic often return nothing. We currently have no idea why.

Bug reports, patches, new modules etc, contact:

	Don Stewart <dons@cse.unsw.edu.au>
	aka dons on #haskell

